law.text:
The department shall promulgate administrative regulations pursuant to KRS Chapter 13A to establish requirements and to set forth standards for household goods carriers, including but not limited to the:
Determination of weights;
Establishment of rates for accessorial services;
Types of discounts prohibited;
Prohibition against a carrier acting as an agent for another carrier;
Insurance provisions;
Information required on a receipt or bill of lading;
Information required on a freight bill;
Liability of carriers;
Estimation of charges;
Absorption or advancement of dock charges;
Information for prospective shippers;
Minimum weight shipments; and
Filing of tariffs.
